- RTOS:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F321087yYy4&list=PLEBQazB0HUyQ4hAPU1cJED6t3DU0h34bz&index=1

- opensource library
- preemptive scheduling
- vTaskStartScheduler()

- Task scheduling:
- ISR: interrupt service routine
- every tick processor being interrupted
- highest priority to run
- task creation: ready, running, blocked

Memory:
- task created on a heap
- tasks also can be created in static section
- different allocation schemes are available
- stack/heap size can be checked in runtime
- vPortFree(...)